He was a fan of the play.

669
01:23:54.667 --> 01:23:55.747
A coincidence?

670
01:23:55.792 --> 01:23:57.908
Was failing the mission
a coincidence too?

671
01:23:58.917 --> 01:24:01.784
Don't forget what
you're living for.

672
01:24:02.625 --> 01:24:04.581
Once you forget that.

673
