683
01:26:14.833 --> 01:26:17.575
She was ordered to kill
on her wedding day.

684
01:26:17.667 --> 01:26:19.828
who wouldn't
make that mistake?

685
01:26:20.667 --> 01:26:24.706
Don't confuse yourself.
your marriage is your mission.

686
01:26:25.750 --> 01:26:28.787
