get your shit together!

810
01:41:40.833 --> 01:41:43.745
Sook-hee is a woman
who could die at any moment.

811
01:41:45.583 --> 01:41:47.574
But I love her.

812
01:41:49.875 --> 01:41:50.955
Sook-hee...

813
01:41:52.958 --> 01:41:56.826
She can't live with blood
on her hands forever.

814
01:42:00.125 --> 01:42:02.912
ldidn't want you
to end up like me.

815
01:43:14.833 --> 01:43:15.913
Cease fire!

816
01:43:20.583 --> 01:43:22.744
Go check it out.

817
01:44:49.583 --> 01:44:50.789
Boss. we're out of ammo!

818
01:46:03.708 --> 01:46:04.914
Mister.

819
01:46:06.792 --> 01:46:08.874
Even for a split second.

820
01:46:12.667 --> 01:46:14.828
did you ever love me?

821
01:46:16.958 --> 01:46:19.745
Nothing we can say now.

822
01:46:22.750 --> 01:46:24.706
will change anything.

823
01:46:26.333 --> 01:46:28.699
I need to hear it.

824
01:46:29.667 --> 01:46:31.658
from your mouth.

825
01:46:39.583 --> 01:46:40.823
Sook-hee...

826
01:46:47.833 --> 01:46:49.915
loved you.

827
01:46:51.750 --> 01:46:56.574
But for the crime
of killing your father.

828
01:46:58.667 --> 01:47:00.908
I couldn't love you anymore.

829
01:47:09.667 --> 01:47:11.908
Is that what you
wanted to hear?

830
01:47:18.625 --> 01:47:20.786
You want to believe that.

831
01:47:22.625 --> 01:47:25.788
You can choose to
live on believing that.

832
01:47:33.833 --> 01:47:36.825
How could you do this to me?

833
01:47:40.833 --> 01:47:42.869
l have that privilege.

834
01:47:45.667 --> 01:47:49.910
Because I made you.

835
01:47:54.542 --> 01:47:56.624
Let me show you.

836
01:47:58.917 --> 01:48:01.784
What you made me into.

837
01:49:31.917 --> 01:49:32.827
Boss!

838
01:49:32.917 --> 01:49:35.659
Boss! Cops are on the way!

839
01:49:36.625 --> 01:49:37.740
- Hurry!
- Yes. sir!

840
01:49:37.875 --> 01:49:39.536
Come on!

841
01:49:40.625 --> 01:49:41.364
Hurry!

842
01:49:41.625 --> 01:49:42.614
Get off!

843
01:49:43.833 --> 01:49:45.573
What is it?

844
01:49:45.792 --> 01:49:46.656
Get off now!

845
01:49:46.750 --> 01:49:47.865
Get the hell off!

846
01:49:48.750 --> 01:49:49.830
Boss. hurry!

847
01:49:49.917 --> 01:49:50.906
Hurry up!

848
01:49:56.792 --> 01:49:58.578
Boss. please hop on!

849
01:50:01.958 --> 01:50:04.745
Please! Boss!

850
01:50:04.917 --> 01:50:07.624
Boss. come quick!

851
01:50:30.875 --> 01:50:32.581
Are you alright?

852
01:51:41.917 --> 01:51:43.578
What the fuck?!

853
01:51:45.667 --> 01:51:46.702
Get rid of her!

854
01:51:51.625 --> 01:51:52.614
Bitch!

855
01:56:51.042 --> 01:56:52.657
Sook-hee...

856
01:56:55.667 --> 01:56:57.703
Why are you shaking?

857
01:57:00.000 --> 01:57:01.706
Pathetic.

858
01:57:05.792 --> 01:57:07.748
Don't be scared.

859
01:57:11.458 --> 01:57:13.574
Don't be scared.

860
01:57:18.042 --> 01:57:19.748
Hit me!

861
01:57:21.500 --> 01:57:22.865
Kill me!

862
01:57:24.958 --> 01:57:26.744
That's when...

863
01:57:29.625 --> 01:57:31.741
it really begins.

864
01:57:36.000 --> 01:57:37.911
The real pain.

865
01:57:41.667 --> 01:57:47.947
Like the day I killed you.

866
01:59:13.625 --> 01:59:17.823
DIRECTOR JUNG Byung-gil

